channel.description:
ITS SO ANNOYING I'VE TRIED MY BEST TO MAKE AS MANY POSTS AND PUT LINKS OUT AND STUFF AND NO ONE WANTS TO HELP. THIS IS MY PROBLEM.... Both Problems shown on this video.... Video Link: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nO5r1lA09gA
Problem 1: Okay, so on ANY Client or Server, ill be able to go on it, move or attack somewhere or something on the server, but when I move the second time it crashes and gets out of it....I think it might have something to do with Java.
Problem 2(Please Just Get The First Problem Solved im desperate for that to work) After I click Start Server, I try to log on my own server, then it says im already logged in. This is what is says on the Console: Registering user 10att10 with pass ********* Server: hybridscape Server (2): Exception! Server: ClientHandler: Client 10att10 disconnected. [03:21:37] Couldn't open output stream to log file 10att10-20090925.log [03:21:37] [03:21:37] Logging into (10att10, *****) [03:21:37] Your UID is: 23176282 Server: ClientHandler: Accepted from 127.0.0.1:49908 Did not save for 10att10 Server: ClientHandler: Client 10att10 disconnected. .....Thats what it says.....
Thanks Guys.
